## Example 23c/d) (powerset of the empty set)

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{set_theory}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  powerset @ null = set_set @ null
).
""" |> prove

res |> format_result |> IO.puts
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{leibniz1}
#{set_theory}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  l @ (powerset @ null) @ (set_set_l1 @ null)
).
""" |> prove

res |> format_result |> IO.puts
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{leibniz2}
#{set_theory}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  l @ (powerset @ null) @ (set_set_l2 @ null)
).
""" |> prove

res |> format_result |> IO.puts
```

